              "description": "<p>Module automatically boots when power is applied, no further command is needed.</p><p>To enter PSM (power save mode), you need to do the following :</p><ol><li>Request timers from the network</li><li>Register on the network</li><li>Pull the <code>RTS</code> pin logic - level <code>HIGH</code> - device will enter PSM a minimum of 100s later</li></ol><p>To exit PSM, you need to do the following :</p><ol><li>Pull the <code>RTS</code> pin logic - level <code>LOW</code></li></ol>",
